title: Ranking the Most Likely Scenarios for the Top Five Picks | Big Board
description:
'The Ringer Fantasy Football Show' hosts Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly project who they think the top five picks will be (3:05). Then they rank the likelihood of each of those scenarios happening (43:21).

Follow ‘The Ringer Fantasy Football Show’ for full episodes.
